Novoic Storyteller Data

Source: R/data.R
RMT_STORYTELLER.Rd

Novoic Storyteller Data data. More information is available at https://adni.loni.usc.edu/data-samples/adni-data/

Usage

data(RMT_STORYTELLER)

Format

A data frame with 10486 observations and 219 variables.

Source

https://adni.loni.usc.edu/data-samples/adni-data/

Details

  • RMT_PHASE character Phase of the study in which this observation was collected , with options: ADNI4

  • ADNIOnlineID character Participant Identifier for the Remote Cohort

  • PTID character Participant Identifier for the in-clinic ADNI study (if applicable)

  • RMT_Timepoint character Timepoint of observation , with options: m00, m06, m12, m18

  • EXAMDATE Date of examination Date: YYY-MM-DD

  • SCREENER_SCORE numeric Overall G-match score for the screener Range value: 0, ..., 100

  • SCREENER_RECOMMEND numeric Overall recommendation for the screener 0=No ; 1=Yes

  • QC_ATTEMPTS numeric Number of attempts at the quality control task Range value: 1, ..., 5

  • QC_PASSED numeric Whether the quality control task was passed 0=No ; 1=Yes

  • USER_AGENT character User agent string

  • STORY1IMM_LANGUAGE character Language for story 1 immediate recall , with options: en-US

  • STORY1IMM_PLAYBACK_COUNT numeric Audio stimulus playback count for story 1 immediate recall Range value: 0, ..., 5

  • STORY1IMM_AUDIO_LENGTH numeric Participant audio length for story 1 immediate recall Range value: 0.76, ..., 270.64
